commit.message:
Update config file with grace periods in all cases

Before this commit the config was not updated with grace period data
unless something else was being updated in the file already.

E.g. HOTP always updates the file, as does using an emergency code.

Fixes #193

Exit with code 1 only if build-rpm fails

Fixes #183
Add more logging for config updates

Shorten syslog name to work with rsyslog

Fixes #172

Clarify use of this PAM module project

Closes #158
